Package it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.commands

Class CommonCommandParsingTest

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.commands.CommonCommandParsingTest
class CommonCommandParsingTest extends Object
Test class that tests paring of all JsonObject attributes common between all AbstractCommand classes. Classes are fetched dynamically using reflection from it.polimi.ingsw.server.controller.commands and tested for all failure points regarding: "gameId", "type" and "username" properties.
